    <string name="help.title">Help</string>
    <string name="help.about">Rewave App helps you control presentations with natural gestures.
        Single Tap to go forward, Double Tap to go back.</string>

    <string name="help.discover.title">Discovering Servers</string>
    <string name="help.discover.body">To control a computer, simply choose discover devices and
        click the desired machine. Make sure that Rewave Server is running on that machine.
        The server can be downloaded for free from http://rewaveapp.com </string>

    <string name="help.connect.title">Connecting</string>
    <string name="help.connect.body">When server is running on the computer, tap it\'s name on your
        phone to connect to it. In case of no \"Server not running\" message start the server. If the
        server is running, try to reconnect.</string>

    <string name="help.control.title">Controlling</string>
    <string name="help.control.body">Once connected, open up your presentation
        (ppt, google docs, pdf, slideshare etc) and single tap to go forward, double tap to go back.</string>

